physical_appearance: This is a photograph of a timber yard in Rangoon. The photograph features a plot of land, with numerous wood logs on the ground. There are seven men on elephants. They are accompanied by several other men standing amongst them, with one men in the middle dressed in a suit and hat. The title is written at the bottom, below the photograph.
title_text: Photograph album of views and portraits in the Punjab, Cashmere, Ceylon, Burma, Penang, Singapore, and Java Bombay Burma Trading Company's Timber Yard, Dallah, Rangoon.
subject_terms_2: Photographs Thomson, J. (John), 1837-1921 Bombay Burmah Trading Corporation Timber Lumber-yards
